  "text": "<Teleport> content not be removed on onDeactivated & not re-insert on onActivated\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3.4.29\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\n[minimal reproduction](https://play.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/169b535b-4af7-4f6d-a746-fc15933c9145)\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2f6001c6-2731-464a-8f88-3c3dc0907494)\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c18d14df-6195-4f5a-b763-d6b3967b8d80)\r\n![Vite App - 个人 - Microsoft​ Edge 2024-07-20 13-54-4820247201357231](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/81fedf0f-6d1f-4388-bc53-f2ae1d20bfd8)\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n\\<Teleport\\> content can be removed on onDeactivated & re-insert on onActivated\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\n\\<Teleport\\> content not be removed on onDeactivated & not re-insert on onActivated\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
